title: The Chaff
description: In an effort to get Teen Titan Go! canceled, Control Freak shows off some deleted scenes.

title: El dia divertido de Falafel
description: Cuando Falafel decide empacar sus cosas e ir a la ciudad, Manzana y Cebollín deben convencerlo de quedarse.

title: Pajama Pajimjams
description: Oscar pretends to be a talking pair of pajamas named "Jimjams" to make his friend Pajamas happy.

title: Welcome to Zombozo-Zone!
description: During medieval times, Team Tennyson must fight to remember that they're not in the past at all, but actually at a Renaissance-esque faire, where "King Zombozo" has hypnotized its guests into thinking they live in the past!

title: Part 1 - Legacy
description: Nya helps Zane backup memories of their adventures to the Samurai X Cave computer, but Zane encounters a mysterious puzzle buried deep within his code.

title: RMS & Brandon's First Episode
description: A Real Magic Skeleton discovers a new job opportunity.

title: Time Share
description: Batman and Blue Beetle have to travel back in time to stop Chronos from destroying a young Dark Knight on his very first case.

title: Terminal Velocity Part 1
description: While Windblade is away on a mission, Bee decides to relive a fun memory.

title: Itch to Explore
description: Craig's quest to map the entire Creek takes him and his friends into the treacherous Poison Ivy Grove.

title: Zombie King
description: Grundy escapes his Louisiana prison intent on using a magical crystal which will allow him to raise the dead from their graves. Only Batman and Swamp thing stand in the way of his growing zombie army.

title: Sick as a Bot
description: After the Energon seeking WINGCODE infects the Autobots with a virus, Bulkhead joins Grimlock in his frantic hunt for the Decepticon. But to capture the 'Con, the duo of brawny Bots has to learn to keep their cool and come up with a workable plan.

title: Alone Quest
description: Craig has an "emergency" leaving Kelsey alone at the Stump.

title: The Metric System vs. Freedom
description: Robin teaches the other Titans about the difference between the Imperial System and the Metric System.

title: Part 3 - Legendary Places
description: Cole joins Jay and Zane inside the Nindroid to solve a mysterious puzzle by revisiting some of Ninjago's distinctive destinations.

title: Classic Rock
description: Batman thinks he's helping a homeless old man who is being mugged on the street only to discover that the man is a powerful wizard being chased by demons in disguise. It turns out the wizard is on a mission to save Shazam from the clutches of Black Adam.

title: Oh, Daisy!
description: Buttercup is not a fan of Bubbles' newly created digital assistant.

title: Secret Swapper of Doom
description: When the girls get a Paper Fortune Teller that can predict the future if they tell it a secret, they begin to rely on it to predict everything. But when it predicts the Powerpuff Girls will be destroyed, the girls must find a way to stop the future from happening.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Love Songs
description: The Titans follow their heart with songs devoted to their greatest relationships: Beast Boy & Raven, Cyborg & Jinx and the Titans & Food.

title: Memory Part 1
description: Windblade tries to help Bumbleebee but he is wary of this "stranger".

title: Strange Nedfellows
description: Omnibus hires the Warriors to get a one-of-a-kind salmon for his fancy aquarium, but Neddy joins them on their quest and wants the "Queen Sal," yet Man Fish the Fish Man wants the salmon to stay in the Fickle Sea!

title: Speed Demon/Mojo Jonesin'
description: Mojo Jonesin':  When the children of Pokey Oaks become envious of the girls' superpowers, a mysterious figure offers them Chemical X. Now, the girls must fight their own classmates who have powers equal to their own./Speed Demon: The girls accidentally fly at the speed of light and when they arrive home, everything has changed. Fifty years have passed and the world has been taken over by Him.

title: #SweetJustice Part 3
description: When six ordinary girls meet and discover that they each have extraordinary powers, they decide to join forces to take on one of Metropolis's most sinister villains.

title: Tips
description: Apple and Onion have to find a way to ride the Hot Air Balloon which is in their town for one day only.

title: Easter Creeps
description: It's Easter and the Tooth Fairy is trying to take over the holiday.

title: Top of the Titans:  Raddest Songs
description: From "Booty Scooty" to "Sour Grapes" to "The Night Begins to Shine," Birdarang is here to count down the raddest music from Teen Titans Go!

title: Teletraan X Part 2
description: Investigating a signal in an abandoned missile silo, Bee and Windblade discover their computer back up drone Teletraan X, but it's a trap!

title: Matrix of Leadership Part 1
description: With Windblade captured by the Seekers, Bumblebee is on his own for the first time and is responsible for saving Cybertron.

title: Innervasion Part 3: Strange Bedfellows
description: After the Junkbot shoots the Omnitrix and it begins glowing neon-blue, an imprisoned Vilgax explains it is now a gateway through which the Fulmini Empire will invade Earth, but the only way to stop them is from within the Omnitrix, so Ben must team up with the ultimate baddie if he is to save his planet.

title: Top of the Titans: Beast Boy & Cyborg Songs
description: Birdarang counts down the best musical moments from the raddest bros you know, Beast Boy and Cyborg. Waffles!

title: Artesanias traviesas
description: Cuando, por accidente, Vic libera al señor de las travesuras del interior una reliquia antigua, V y V tienen que trabajar en equipo para volver a encerrarlo.

title: Bad Man Oldman
description: When the Warriors re-thatch Old Man Oldman's roof and absentmindedly make it look like Prohyas' hair, Oldman dons an giant evil toupee exacts his revenge!

title: Half-Sies
description: During a trip to the Lake of the Ozarks, Ben and Gwen squabble over Ben's unnecessary "half-birthday" celebration, but when Max gets word of a suspicious rockslide nearby, the cousins must put aside their differences if they are to rescue the trapped miners and uncover who is behind the manmade catastrophe before it's too late: the Bugg Brothers.

title: Part 7 - Beasts and Dragons
description: Jay, Kai and Zane remember some of Ninjago's most fearsome creatures in order to help Cole defend the cave from an unidentified monster.

title: Stay Goth, Poodle Girl, Stay Goth
description: Gwen accidentally brings a pink stuffed pony she loves to daycare and spends the day denying it's hers.

title: Whiteout Part 2
description: Windblade flies to the Himalayas to investigate while Bee watches television, acquiring new verbal "samples".

title: Lego DC Super Hero Girls: Brain Drain
description: Missing memories provide an intriguing mystery for everyone's favorite young female heroes in this all-new animated film.  When Supergirl, Wonder Woman, Batgirl, Harley Quinn, Bumblebee, Poison Ivy and Katana suddenly realize they cannot remember a single moment from their Monday at Super Hero High, the young Super Heroes spring into sleuthing action! Suspecting foul-play, they band together to retrace their steps and uncover the mystery of who exactly stole their memories - and, what nefarious plan might be afoot?

title: Dog Daze/In Focus
description: Dog Daze: Lightning discovers a new Bakugan, Artulean, leading to an unhealthy rivalry with Howlkor./In Focus: While Lia's newswoman mom does an expose on the AO Strata the Hunter tries to capture Hydorous.

title: I Used to Be a Peoples
description: Robin feels the other Titans are spending too much time together so he encourages them to spend some time alone.

title: The Big Sleep
description: When the Professor's latest invention wreaks havoc in the house, it's up to the Powerpuff Girls to stop it before it escapes.

title: Innervasion Part 4: Mind over Alien Matter
description: While inside the Omnitrix, Ben and Vilgax must work together if they are to close the gateway, but once the Fulmini leader, the High Override, appears, even that might not be enough. Luckily, help arrives in the form of a being calling itself Glitch!

title: Show Don't Tell
description: Ben, Gwen, and Grandpa Max arrive at a Native American national park to witness the Ayasha Plinths, an ancient Stonehenge-like rock formation. But when the sinister sorcerer Hex arrives, Ben must battle against a beast Hex magically made out of huge rocks!

title: Throwing Shade Part 2
description: Mega Man stops Fire Man by replicating his powers and fighting fire with fire. Unfortunately, Mega Man also learns that he can replicate a robot's mental state as well, and must get his own anger under control to win. Defeated, Fire Man reports back to his secret master, Sgt. Night!

title: Folk Art Foes
description: When Vic accidently unleashes the lord of mischief from an ancient relic, V and V have to work together to trap it back inside.

title: Silent Treatment/Sweet 'n' Sour
description: The Silent Treatment: When the girls go to see a silent movie with the Professor, they end up getting pulled into the film by an old-time villain./Sweet 'n' Sour: The girls must figure out how to beat Townsville's newest band of criminals: a group of adorable little animals.

title: Part 9 - Prophecy of the Green Ninja
description: The final puzzle forces each ninja to question the true meaning of the Green Ninja Prophecy, but success is not what it seems.

title: Top of the Titans: Dance Party!
description: Come correct because it's a Titans Dance Battle! Birdarang reviews the greatest dance songs in Teen Titans Go! history.

title: Blast Resort
description: Mega Man must assist Blasto Woman in a heist to stop a powerful EMP emitter from falling into the wrong hands.

title: Subterranean Homesick Blues/Honey Struck
description: Subterranean Homesick Blues: The AO return home to learn that no time has passed but they soon discover their knowledge of brawling has gotten years more advanced./Honey Struck: After Strata is sent packing the AO discover that they have picked up a hitchhiker a Panda-like Bakugan who is nothing but sticky trouble.

title: Part 6 - The Elemental Masters
description: A riddle requires the Ninja to consider the powers and history of the Elemental Masters. Meanwhile, Nya struggles to keep the power on in the Samurai X Cave.

title: Superfriends
description: The new girl next door learns it's hard to be best friends with superheroes and soon starts hanging out with the wrong kind of kid, Princess.

title: Sabotage Part 2
description: Shockwave creates false memories designed to convince Bee he was always a Decepticon spy.

title: The First Day
description: Best friends Oscar and Hedgehog get dropped off at their first day at summer camp.

title: Enemy of My Enemy
description: When Optimus returns with old friends and dire warnings of a Cybertronian invasion of Earth, the Autobots must split up to defend their old home and their new one, with the Bee Team returning to Cybertron, while Optimus and his All-Stars stay behind to defend against the invasion's advanced force.

title: Teletraan X Part 1
description: The Decepticon Armada is nearing Earth to seek the Allspark and are desperate for clues.

title: Apple's in Trouble
description: Apple is challenged to a fight by a grumpy Cheesesteak, so he and Onion go on a quest to find the source of Cheesesteak's grumpiness.

title: Part 10 - Greatest Battles
description: Solving the puzzles releases a new peril for the Ninja to face. Will memories of their greatest victories be enough to defeat it?

title: Follow that Space Cab!
description: While Superman escorts his prisoner Mr. Mind between planets, he is attacked by Lobo who wants to collect a reward on Mind. Temporarily powered-down, Superman seeks Space Cabbie's help to get away from Lobo.

title: Night of the Bat
description: Superman and other Justice League members have to battle Batman when he gets possessed by an evil Djinn, Uthool, who is intent on using the JL power core to blow a crack in Earth.

title: Part 8 - Rise of Garmadon
description: The Ninja confront memories of their greatest villain and ally, Garmadon, before the threat to Zane controls him completely.

title: Cube Part 2
description: Windblade finds it hard to believe that Bee can't remember his favorite sport, Cube!

title: Matter of the Mind/Core Cell
description: Matter of Mind: Drago leads the Bakugan against the threat of Tiko to protect a powerful energy source called the Core Cell./Core Cell: The AO defend the Core Cell from an attack by Tiko and in a last ditch effort to save it Dan manages to evolve Drago into his L2 form.

title: The Extinction Event Part 2
description: Shockwave orders the Seekers to help him create an extinction event and destroy all organic life on the planet.

title: Let's Watch the Pilot
description: KO, Rad, and Enid look back at the Lakewood Plaza Turbo pilot.

title: Sabotage Part 1
description: From his lab on Cybertron, Shockwave launches an attack on Bee's most vulnerable place...his memories.

title: Dead Ringer
description: When Vic doesn't pick Val for his soccer team, Val vows to win with his own squad. But when his team doesn't match up, he resorts to supernatural means to win.

title: Chocolate Money Badgers
description: Oscar learns that he can earn merit badges that unlock prizes.

title: #AdventuresInBunnysitting
description: Zee asks Kara to look after her two magical bunnies, which quickly start to multiply, wreaking havoc all across Metropolis.

title: The Journey Part 2
description: The Autobots are nearly out of Energon, so they land on a dark planet where they encounter subterranean creatures.

title: Siloed Part 1
description: Windblade is playing Cube on Cybertron with Bee when she realizes these are memories and she is still held captive by Slipstream.

title: Cube Part 1
description: Bee discovers a mysterious object in the stolen Decepticon shuttle.

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Super Hero High
description: Supergirl arrives at Super Hero High and struggles to learn to control her new powers. Meanwhile, the Junior Detective Club investigates a mysterious rash of security breaches centered around the teleportation Boom Tubes.

title: Jessica Goes to the Creek
description: When Craig and Jessica are locked out of the house, Craig has no choice but to bring his little sister to the Creek.

title: King of the Dinosaurs Part 1
description: With the help of Teletraan- X, Bee and Windblade excavate an deactivated Autobot that looks like a dinosaur.

title: Grup Jam
description: Grup invents the "new" sport of basketball, but the stakes are too high for the Warriors to let him play the Galacton team, as the winner shall rule the Kingdom of Rhyboflaven.

title: Moral Decay/Meet the Beat Alls
description: Moral Decay: When Bubbles loses a tooth, she gets a shiny coin under her pillow the next day. Buttercup sees a gold mine in the mouths of Townsville's criminal element./Meet the Beat Alls: Mojo, Him, Princess and Fuzzy band together to form the Bad Four, a criminal supergroup out to destroy the Powerpuff Girls. Everything is going great until Mojo meets Moko Jono and falls in love.

title: You're It
description: A vicious game of tag wreaks havoc on the Creek, claiming Kelsey as the next it.

title: Matrix of Leadership Part 2
description: Bumblebee doubts his abilities as he has to find the Ark to awaken Optimus and the Autobots.

title: Presenting Joe Cuppa
description: KO tries to help his favorite comedian, Joe Cuppa.

title: #SweetJustice Part 4
description: When six ordinary girls meet and discover that they each have extraordinary powers, they decide to join forces to take on one of Metropolis's most sinister villains.

title: Manzana esta en Problemas
description: Bistec con Queso, malhumorado, desafía a Manzana a una pelea. De ese modo, Manzana puede embarcarse con Cebollín en una misión para encontrar el origen del malhumor de Bistec con Queso.

title: A New Life
description: Apple and Onion both leave their homes and follow their dreams to the big city but things don't go quite to plan.

title: Perfect Moment
description: When Hawkodile admits his love for Dr. Fox, Unikitty and the gang become his love gurus to help him confess his feelings for her. Unfortunately, Unikitty's grand plans for the perfect moment of love complicates everything.

title: Convencion de Rath
description: De regreso en casa, Ben no puede inscribirse en un concurso de cosplay de gatos sin su propio disfraz. Pero cuando se convierte en Rath, un nuevo alienígena con aspecto felino y mal carácter, el lado salvaje que Ben acaba de descubrir pronto tendrá resultados inesperados.

title: Awaken Sleeping Giants Part 1
description: Bee, Windblade and Grimlock finally determine the location of the lost ship, the Ark.

title: The Exit/The Lost and the Cost
description: The Exit: The AO compete with a rival Brawling team for ViewTube hits leading to a "winner take all" brawl./The Lost and the Cost: Everett Ray, a promotor, tries to get the AO to join an official league for Bakugan Battling.

title: Maccadam's Part 2
description: Windblade realizes Bee's memory must be coming back - they access the Hivemind and visit three different eras of Maccadam's.

title: The Perfect Team
description: Onion worries his relationship with Apple is in jeopardy when a stray cat enters the picture.

title: Allspark Part 2
description: They search for clues as to the whereabouts of the Allspark and uncover another important memory!

title: Saxophone Come Home
description: Oscar befriends a teenage Yeti.

title: Who Took Toast
description: When Toast disappears from Unikitty's party she leads a search to find him and expose the toast-napper.

title: Futbol a Muerte
description: Cuando Vic no elige a Val para su equipo de fútbol, Val promete ganar con su propio equipo. Pero cuando su equipo no está a la altura, recurre a medios sobrenaturales para ganar.

title: King of the Dinosaurs Part 2
description: Teletraan-X's scans reveal their old friend Grimlock, who is intent on finding the rest of his missing dinosaur friends.

title: Fractured Part 1
description: Windblade discovers Bumblebee in the desert on his own.

title: Part 2 - Vehicles and Mechs
description: Nya digitizes Jay and uploads him into Zane's mind.  Jay reviews memories of the Ninja's various motorcycles, mechs and planes in order to solve the vehicle themed puzzle.

title: Gum and Gummer
description: Beth gets her gum stuck in Leshawna's hair and has to get it out - without Leshawna finding out it's there.

title: #SweetJustice Part 1
description: When six ordinary girls meet and discover that they each have extraordinary powers, they decide to join forces to take on one of Metropolis's most sinister villains.

title: Part 5 - The Digiverse and Beyond
description: The team tackles a puzzle about technology in Ninjago while the threat to Zane grows graver by the minute.

title: King of the Hill Part 2
description: The harried Autobots' Stunticon enemy proves more formidable and crafty than they anticipated, using his guided missiles to threaten a nuclear waste disposal site.

title: Siloed Part 2
description: Windblade manages to fight her way out when Slipstream is called away and she discovers Bee and Teletraan-X are there to help!

title: Megatron Is My Hero Part 2
description: Bee remembers an early version of Megatron where he was a gladiatorial hero, but realizes how dangerous he became.

title: Megatron Is My Hero Part 1
description: Windblade explains the threat of Megatron and the Decepticons to Bee.

title: Collateral Damage
description: Soundwave finally escapes the Shadow Zone to set up a Beacon Generator intended to summon Megatron! While the Bee Team engages the notorious Decepticon atop a skyscraper, Optimus Prime takes on Laserbeak in the skies over Crown City, and Sideswipe learns a lesson in considering the consequences of his actions.

title: Innervasion Part 2: Call the Dream Police
description: After defeating the Warbot and discovering Vilgax inside, Ben's "secret voices" only worsen and begin affecting his sleep, but once Gwen discovers a sleepwalking Ben using missing items from the campsite to create his own massive Junkbot, it is up to Ben to stop his own creation.

title: Yuri and the Bear
description: Baby Ice Bear lives alone in the arctic and meets a mysterious man named Yuri. Together they help each other survive the cold environment.

title: Eruption Part 1
description: As the Autobots discover the Ark, they have to wake up their friends in this battle for the future.

title: El Equipo Perfecto
description: A Cebollín le preocupa que su relación con Manzana corra peligro cuando un gato callejero entra en su vida.

title: Fire Man in the Hole
description: While hiking on a dormant volcano, Aki sets out to retrieve Ashley's lost camera and, as Mega Man, to stop Fire Man from setting off an eruption!

title: Propinas
description: Luego de destruir por accidente el boleto de Falafel para un concierto, Manzana y Cebollín deben descubrir un modo de evitar la furia de Falafel.

title: #SweetJustice Part 2
description: When six ordinary girls meet and discover that they each have extraordinary powers, they decide to join forces to take on one of Metropolis's most sinister villains.

title: P.L.O.T. Device
description: When boredom levels in the castle hit dangerously high levels, Dr. Fox conveniently introduces her P.L.O.T. Device. When pressed, this device alters reality to make it more exciting. Richard warns that this might be dangerous, but no one listens. It's not long till he is proven correct and life in the castle becomes dangerously exciting.

title: The Journey Part 1
description: Bee accesses a memory from onboard the Ark on its journey from Cybertron to Earth.

title: Baby Orphan Ninja Bears
description: The Baby Bears venture into the sewers and meet a ninja-like martial arts master.

title: Shadowstriker Part 1
description: Bee doubts his fighting abilities as he continually loses in practice to Windblade.

title: Share and Share Dislike
description: Super Shooting Star Magisword is the coolest Magisword ever, but Vambre and Prohyas can't seem to share it, and even a quest to reclaim the never-melting ice cube back from Frosteratu can't shake their obsession.

title: Just Another Manic Mojo/Mime for a Change
description: Just Another Manic Mojo: The Powerpuff Girls lose their baseball in Mojo's house, offering him the perfect opportunity to destroy these pesky superheroines if he can only get them to sit still./Mime for a Change: An accidental bleach spill turns Rainbow the Clown into the malevolent Mr. Mime. He proceeds to turn Townsville black and white and dead all over.

title: Uncle Easter
description: The Easter Bunny, unable to fulfill his egg-delivering duties, has Uncle Grandpa fill in for him.

title: Whiteout Part 1
description: Bee remembers his escape pod from the Ark crashed in the snowy Himalayas.

title: The Teen Titans Go Easter Holiday Classic
description: The Easter Bunny is missing, and it's up to the Titans to find him before Easter is ruined.

title: Allspark Part 1
description: Hiding from the Decepticons, Windblade use her Cityspeaker powers to search Bee's memory files.

title: Lego DC Super Hero Girls: Galactic Wonder
description: Wonder Woman has won student of the month at Super Hero High again!  As a special surprise Principal Waller has flown in Wonder Woman's mother, Queen Hippolyta, for a visit. Queen Hippolyta is not happy with what she finds and demands that Wonder Woman return to school at the island paradise of Themyscira. Hoping to take her mind off of her troubles with her mother Wonder Woman, Batgirl and Supergirl decide to investigate a strange electromagnetic anomaly. Their investigation leads them to the hideout of Lena Luthor where they discover a plot between her and Eclipso to transform the planet Earth into a new version of Gemworld!  The girls will have to split up to find the generators scattered around the planet and destroy them. They'll also have to overcome Lena's new breed of mood altering Kryptomites to save the day and convince Queen Hippolyta that Super Hero High is the best school for Wonder Woman!

title: Part 4 - Ninjago's Most Wanted
description: Kai enters Zane's mind and suggests the Ninja take a break from puzzle-solving to figure out which villain is trying to hack their friend.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Rivals
description: From Trigon to Terra to Darkseid, Robin counts down the worst of the worst: the greatest villains to ever challenge the Teen Titans!

title: Eruption Part 2
description: Teletraan-X has to reboot the offline computer systems to wake up their Autobot friends and the ship while fighting the Deceptions.

title: The Audition
description: The Bears audition to be the next mascot for their favorite cereal. They get so caught up in the process that their competitiveness gets the best of them.

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Intergalactic Games
description: Super Hero High is facing off against Korugar Academy in the Intergalactic Games, but Lena Luthor takes advantage of the gathering of supers to enact her villainous plan.

title: Shadowstriker Part 2
description: Through memory, Bee is shown some of his past triumphs, like rescuing Optimus from Shadowstriker.

title: The Extinction Event Part 1
description: Decepticons Shockwave and Shadowstriker arrive on Earth with a simple plan to find the Allspark.

title: Falafel's Fun Day
description: When Falafel decides to pack up and leave the city, Apple and Onion have to convince him to stay or they'll have to leave too.

title: #SweetJustice
description: When six ordinary girls meet and discover that they each have extraordinary powers, they decide to join forces to take on one of Metropolis's most sinister villains.

title: Derby Dollies
description: When Bubbles joins the Derbytantes, Buttercup finds herself on the sidelines.

title: Awaken Sleeping Giants Part 2
description: Slipstream and her Seekers engage in battle as our heroes trek towards the Ark.

title: Terminal Velocity Part 2
description: Bee finds himself on Velocitron with Hod Rod to have some fun but it turns into a nightmare as the Plague of Rust descends.

title: Too Much Is Never Enough
description: Envious of Namagem's ability to wield more than three powers at a time, Mega Man tries taking all of his replicated schematics on board, with grave side effects.

title: Mr. Moon/What's Wrong with Dan
description: Mr. Moon: Wynton finds a new Bakugan who proves difficult to control but things get more complicated when Col. Tripp seizes control of Trox./What's Wrong with Dan: With "Dan" behaving strangely toward the AO Lightning sniffs out the truth- an impostor!

title: Polos Opuestos
description: Un viaje al Polo Sur queda patas arriba cuando el equipo Tennyson aterriza en el Polo Norte. Pero Ben rápidamente descubre a los culpables: iSolar y Polar Twain, unos científicos con poder magnético que quieren chantajear al mundo amenazando con invertir los polos magnéticos de la Tierra!

title: Maccadam's Part 1
description: Bee and Windblade avoid an attack by Slipstream and Bee asks to go to Maccadam's!

title: Innervasion Part 1: Message in a Boxcar
description: As Team Tennyson prepares their boxcar for an upcoming race, Ben is hearing voices and is unable to go Upgrade to enhance his car, but once the race is interrupted by a mysterious Warbot, Ben must overcome the voices inside his head if he is to defeat the giant adversary.

title: Brain Freeze
description: When a mysterious new ice cream flavor takes Townsville by storm, the girls suspect there might be foul play.

title: Fractured Part 2
description: Windblade realizes Bumblebee does not remember her and her mission to find the Allspark is critical.

title: Action Comedy
description: Rhyboflaven's local fictional superhero, Broccoli Punch, has an all-new, spectacular action stage show, but when Flonk masquerades as the star, the Warriors disguise themselves as broccoli bad guys to teach the imposter a lesson!

title: Throwing Shade Part 1
description: Sgt. Night publicly criticizes Dr. Light's views on human & robot unity during a school assembly, invoking the ire of Fire Man and forcing Silicon City's newly minted hero, Mega Man, to intervene.

title: Monster Babies
description: Alice lures Oscar and his monster friends for a tea party, but only to turn the monsters into cute babies.

title: Prisoner Principles
description: Strongarm struggles with the correct way to treat a prisoner while also helping the Bee Team keep Steeljaw and his pack from wreaking havoc at a nuclear power plant.

title: Memory Part 2
description: Windlbade and Bumblebee are attacked by Decepticons and she regains his trust.

title: Una Nueva Vida
description: Manzana y Cebollín abandonan sus hogares y se mudan a la ciudad, donde se conocen por primera vez.
